<eesti>&Uuml;leminek </eesti>
<inglise>Transition </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Koolide p&otilde;hikirjad viiakse k&auml;esoleva seadusega vastavusse kolme kuu jooksul k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumisest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The statutes of schools shall be brought into conformity with this Act within three months after the entry into force of this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>2. Vabariigi Valitsusel korraldada P&otilde;llumajandusministeeriumi valitsemisalasse kuuluvate riigi kutse&otilde;ppeasutuste &uuml;leviimine Haridusministeeriumi valitsemisalasse 2000. aasta 1. septembriks. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Government of the Republic shall organise the transfer of state vocational schools in the area of government of the Ministry of Agriculture to the area of government of the Ministry of Education by 1 September 2000. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) &Otilde;pilastele, kes asusid &otilde;ppima kutse&otilde;ppeasutuses keskerihariduse &otilde;ppekava alusel enne 1999. aastat ja on selle &otilde;ppekava t&auml;ies mahus t&auml;itnud, antakse keskerihariduse omandamist t&otilde;endav l&otilde;putunnistus. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Students who commenced their studies at a vocational educational institution on the basis of a curriculum of vocational secondary education before the year 1999 and have completed the curriculum to the full extent shall be issued a graduation certificate certifying the acquisition of vocational secondary education. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.05.99 j&otilde;ust. 20.06.99 - RT I 1999, 51, 550) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.05.99 entered into force 20.06.99 - RT I 1999, 51, 550) </inglise>
<eesti>(4) &Otilde;pilastele, kes asusid &otilde;ppima kutse&otilde;ppeasutuses p&otilde;hihariduse baasil kutsehariduse &otilde;ppekava alusel enne 1999. aastat ja on selle &otilde;ppekava t&auml;ies mahus t&auml;itnud, antakse p&otilde;hihariduse baasil kutsehariduse omandamist t&otilde;endav l&otilde;putunnistus. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Students who commenced their studies at a vocational educational institution on the basis of basic education and on the basis of a curriculum of vocational education before the year 1999 and have completed the curriculum to the full extent shall be issued a graduation certificate certifying the acquisition of vocational education on the basis of basic education. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.05.99 j&otilde;ust. 20.06.99 - RT I 1999, 51, 550) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.05.99 entered into force 20.06.99 - RT I 1999, 51, 550) </inglise>
<eesti>(5) &Otilde;pilastele, kes asusid &otilde;ppima kutse&otilde;ppeasutuses p&otilde;hihariduse baasil kutse- ja keskhariduse &otilde;ppekava alusel enne 1999. aastat ja on selle &otilde;ppekava t&auml;ies mahus t&auml;itnud, antakse p&otilde;hihariduse baasil kutse- ja keskhariduse omandamist t&otilde;endav l&otilde;putunnistus. </eesti>
<inglise>(5) Students who commenced their studies at a vocational educational institution on the basis of basic education and on the basis of a curriculum of vocational and secondary education before the year 1999 and have completed the curriculum to the full extent shall be issued a graduation certificate certifying the acquisition of vocational and secondary education on the basis of basic education. </inglise>
<eesti>(18.05.99 j&otilde;ust. 20.06.99 - RT I 1999, 51, 550) </eesti>
<inglise>(18.05.99 entered into force 20.06.99 - RT I 1999, 51, 550) </inglise>
