<eesti>Eesti Vabariigi haridusseaduse muutmine ja t&auml;iendamine </eesti>
<inglise>Amendment of Republic of Estonia Education Act </inglise>
<eesti>Eesti Vabariigi haridusseaduses (RT 1992, 12, 192; RT I 1993, 35, 547; 40, 593; 63, 892; 1994, 12, 200; 1995, 12, 119; 16, 228; 23, 333; 58, 1003; 1996, 49, 953; 51, 965; 1997, 42, 678; 81, 1365; 1998, 57, 859; 61, 980; 64/64, 1007; 1999, 10, 150; 24, 358; 51, 550) tehakse j&auml;rgmised muudatused ja t&auml;iendused: </eesti>
<inglise>The Republic of Estonia Education Act (RT 1992, 12, 192; RT I 1993, 35, 547; 40, 593; 63, 892; 1994, 12, 200; 1995, 12, 119; 16, 228; 23, 333; 58, 1003; 1996, 49, 953; 51, 965; 1997, 42, 678; 81, 1365; 1998, 57, 859; 61, 980; 64/64, 1007; 1999, 10, 150; 24, 358; 51, 550) is amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>1) paragrahvi 4 l&otilde;ikes 8 lisatakse p&auml;rast s&otilde;na "p&otilde;hikiri" s&otilde;nad "v&otilde;i p&otilde;him&auml;&auml;rus"; </eesti>
<inglise>1) subsection 4 (8) is amended by adding the words "or the statutes" [ v&otilde;i p&otilde;him&auml;&auml;rus ] after the word "statutes" [ p&otilde;hikiri ]; </inglise>
<eesti>2) paragrahvi 19 l&otilde;ige 1 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>2) subsection 19 (1) is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"(1) &Otilde;ppeasutus on haridusasutus, kus toimub &otilde;petamine ja &otilde;ppimine vastavalt &otilde;ppekavale. </eesti>
<inglise>"(1) A school is an educational institution where teaching and learning are performed on the basis of the curriculum. </inglise>
<eesti>&ldquo;; </eesti>
<inglise>&ldquo;; </inglise>
<eesti>3) paragrahvi 21 l&otilde;ikes 3 asendatakse s&otilde;na "p&otilde;hikirjad" s&otilde;naga "p&otilde;him&auml;&auml;rused"; </eesti>
<inglise>3) in subsection 21 (3) the word "statutes" [ p&otilde;hikirjad ] is substituted by the word "statutes" [ p&otilde;him&auml;&auml;rused ]; </inglise>
<eesti>4) paragrahvi 29 l&otilde;ikes 1 lisatakse p&auml;rast s&otilde;na "p&otilde;hikiri" s&otilde;nad "v&otilde;i p&otilde;him&auml;&auml;rus"; </eesti>
<inglise>4) subsection 29 (1) is amended by adding the words "or the statutes" [ v&otilde;i p&otilde;him&auml;&auml;rus ] after the word "statutes" [ p&otilde;hikiri ]; </inglise>
<eesti>5) paragrahvi 34 l&otilde;ige 2 muudetakse ja s&otilde;nastatakse j&auml;rgmiselt: </eesti>
<inglise>5) subsection 34 (2) is amended and worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"(2) Haridusasutuste pedagoogide t&ouml;&ouml;suhteid reguleerib t&ouml;&ouml;seadusandlus, arvestades teistest &otilde;igusaktidest tulenevaid erisusi." </eesti>
<inglise>"(2) Employment law regulates the employment relations of teachers of educational institutions, taking into account the exceptions arising from other legislation." </inglise>
